description: 
globs: 
alwaysApply: true
---
Component typings must use type instead of interface.
Component typings should be always exported.
Components should be declared with explicit FC notation.
Do not create documentation unless explicitly requested.
The styles cannot be defined inline. If you need to create files of styles, it would be in `styles` folder.
It must be one file for one component and one file for styles of a component.
All code should be created in english.
